data.description: Large renovated ranch in the heart of the City of Snellville , a perfect location for work, dinner out and shopping. Relax on the front porch and enjoy the 1/2 acre lot with mature trees and a small creek in front. Renovated in 2021 with new white kitchen cabinets, vinyl plan flooring throughout except bedrooms with new carpet, new appliances including refrigerator, granite counters, new lighting. Sunny breakfast area with bay window over looking large oversized patio and fenced yard. Formal living room and dining room, 3 large bedrooms, 2 full baths, secondary bath has beautiful new shower. Vinyl plank throughout home with exception of bedrooms where carpet was installed 2021. Roof 2021, waterheater 2021. Home was painted inside and outside, new vinyl garage door and opener. Side entry garage, the home is mostly brick with wood trim. Separate detached shed off of patio is a great shop, craft room, gardening haven! Super place for office or home schooling as well. The building is hardiplank and sits off backyard patio close to home and opens as well to fenced backyard. Quiet neighborhood. A great opportunity to own an afforable home in a great location that is in move in condition.
